headline: 3 Things to Know About Cava Stock Before You Buy
summary: Cava Group (NYSE: CAVA) stock caught investor attention from the time of its initial public offering (IPO) in the middle of 2023, and its stock has soared since.  Cava stock is down 44% from its highs, and it's starting to look more reasonably priced.  Investors have been loving Cava because if it continues to report similar performance to what it's demonstrating now, it has incredible long-term potential.
